        "body": "<p>A family-run shop in Los Angeles, California, online since 2020. We carry wooden toys, Waldorf dolls, and open-ended play sets, sourced from makers we know by name. Each piece is chosen to scale across a childhood, and to last for the sibling who comes after.</p>",
